OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain soon clearing
OL,6,FShetland. Otherwise bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells and scattered showers. Drier
OL,8,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Blustery
OL,9,Fwest to northwest winds, easing
OL,10,Ftowards the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSunny and then clear spells
OL,13,Fwith scattered showers continuing
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,15,FFeeling quite chilly with winds
OL,16,Ffalling light.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FIt will feel rather cold
OL,19,Fwith bright or sunny spells and
OL,20,Fscattered heavy showers through
OL,21,FWednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
