OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FStill
OL,6,Fcold with sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fheavy showers on Thursday and breezy
OL,8,Fat times. Showers and winds ease
OL,9,Fthrough Friday, then mostly dry and
OL,10,Fbright continuing on through Saturday.
